fields.name: Monthly
fields.description: Our gyms are equipped with the very latest tools and machines to help you in your training. We want you to achieve results that can stimulate continuous exercise and good health! So try for one month and carry on for years.

fields.name: Yearly
fields.description: Our gyms are equipped with the very latest tools and machines to help you in your training. We want you to achieve results that can stimulate continuous exercise and good health! So try for one year and carry on for years.

fields.name: Blue
fields.description:
This is where it all begins. When you become a member with us, you 
automatically become a BLUE member, but if you stay for a while, you will soon
get new colors and benefits. The first benefit is that you can bring a friend to the gym
 once a year - completely free!

fields.name: Gold
fields.description:
Get 1 month free. This offer only applies to new
members, ie people who have not been members of
Fitness Wellness in the last 12 months. The membership
returns after 12 months at the regular price (SEK 229 / 
month).

fields.name: Black
fields.description:
Get 1 month free / member you recruit. This offer only
applies to new members, ie people who have not been
members of Fitness24Seven in the past 12 months. 
The membership returns after 12 months at the regular 
price (SEK 229 / month).

fields.name: Weekly Offer
fields.description:
Due to increased demand, we are currently offering unlimited trial training weeks for SEK 99 / week. 
You can take part in this at the nearest gym during staffed hours.

fields.name: Silver
fields.description: Our gyms are equipped with the very latest tools and machines to help you in your training. We want you to achieve results that can stimulate continuous exercise and good health! So extend your membership and become one of our loyal member.

fields.name: Train out in August
fields.description:
ALLINCLUSIVE. No lock-in period or start-up fee.
The offer is valid when you sign up for a current subscription (2 months notice).
You save up to: SEK 625. The offer is valid until June 30.

fields.name: Personal
fields.description: In our gym you can book your personal trainer who will give you personal attension in whole session and help you in exercise.

fields.name: Group
fields.description: Some people loose intersest in gym very easily. They need some motivation to continue. So they prefer to do in groups. Our gym provides group training in which you do gym with other gym members and motivate each other.

fields.name: Online
fields.description: Everyone is different and we want to offer online training that suits everyone, regardless of who you are and what your goals are, member or non-member. We have put together a number of different exercises and sessions with different orientations -choose yourself if you want to focus on one session or if you want to combine several in a row.
